This paper is about a deep learning framework for face rendering, which involves computer vision (CV) and graphics (GR) techniques. The paper also discusses the use of a large dataset and a novel loss function, which are common topics in machine learning (LG) and artificial intelligence (AI). Finally, the paper presents high-quality visual results, which could fall under multimedia (MM). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.MM.
